"A.P.242/2/26/16:30": "...I see. The two clones have joined hands in everlasting friendship."
"Even though they were discarded by the Photoners, they remain attached to their descendants... What utterly foolish creatures."
"My deepest apologies. My pursuit failed, and they have gained new strength..."
"Why do you apologize, Varuna? Even when gathered, dust will never be anything but dust."
"You will continue to act as my loyal and devoted subject. God of Fidelity, Varuna."
"Quna (EP6)'s Partner Card can now be used."
